            "title": "港股初段高位橫行 寧德時代破頂最多彈逾10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今早跟隨外圍高開，加上內地首季經濟增長勝預期，支持大市於高位橫行。寧德時代(03750)績後反彈兼破頂，最多曾漲逾10%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15879382-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%a9%ab%e8%a1%8c-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a%e5%bd%88%e9%80%be10",
