        {
            "title": "內地首季GDP增長5%  勝預期  社會零售增長遜預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國一季度GDP增長5%，勝市場預期，上季度為 4.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">《彭博》綜合市場預測，中國今年第一季經濟增長4.8%，去年第四季增長4.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240304_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240304_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國3月規模以上工業增加值按年增長 5.7%。《彭博》預測按年增長5.3%，</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國3月社會消費品零售總額按年升 1.7%，《彭博》預測零售總額增長2.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首季固定資產投資按年升1.7%，《彭博》預測固定資產投資增長1.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15879283-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3gdp%e5%a0%b15-%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f-%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e9%81%9c%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240305_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 10:11:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在岸人民幣開市報6.8185兑1美元 中間價跌34點子",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兑美元今日開市報6.8185元兌1美元，較上日收市價微升3點子。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民幣中間價則定於6.8616兌1美元，較上日下調34點子。</p>\n</div>",
