        {
            "title": "滬指開市升2點 深成指升47點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段偏好，上證綜指以4030點開市，升2點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14546點，亦升47點或0.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升9點或0.2%，開報4694點；創業板指數開市報3531點，升16點或0.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15879185-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%872%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8747%e9%bb%9e",
